<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
    <title>Account Deletion</title>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            color: #333;
            padding: 10px;
        }
        .card {
            border: none;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            padding: 20px;
        }
        h1 { color: #6C63FF; font-weight: 700; }
        h5 {
            color: #222;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-top: 25px;
            border-left: 4px solid #6C63FF;
            padding-left: 10px;
        }
        p {
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: #555;
            font-size: 14.5px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 576px) {
            body { padding: 5px; }
            .card { padding: 16px; border-radius: 12px; }
            h1 { font-size: 1.6rem; }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="container-fluid my-3">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-12 col-md-10 col-lg-8">
            <div class="card bg-white">

                <!-- Header -->
                <div class="text-center mb-4">
                    <h1 class="mb-2">Account Deletion</h1>
                    <hr style="border-color: #6C63FF; width: 60px; margin: 20px auto; opacity: 1;">
                </div>

                <!-- Content -->
                <div class="content">

                    <p>Users can delete their account directly from the Nova Up application by going to Settings → Delete Account.</p>

                    <h5>What data is deleted</h5>
                    <p>When a user deletes their account, the following data is permanently removed:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Phone number and authentication data</li>
                        <li>User profile information</li>
                        <li>Gym membership and branch association</li>
                        <li>Attendance and QR check-in records</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h5>Deletion process</h5>
                    <p>Account deletion is processed immediately within the application. No external request is required.</p>

                    <h5>Important note</h5>
                    <p>Deletion is irreversible. Once the account is deleted, data cannot be recovered.</p>

                    <h5>Contact</h5>
                    <p>If you face any issue with account deletion, contact support at: <b>saeid.yosri@gmail.com</b></p>

                    <p class="mt-4">This page is provided to comply with Google Play account deletion requirements.</p>

                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
